Ivory Coast Releases as Many as 17 Members of Nation’s Former Ruling Party

-- B y   B a u d e l a i r e   M i e u
-- 
2011-06-20T10:02:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-20/ivory-coast-releases-as-many-as-17-members-of-nation-s-former-ruling-party.html
Ivory Coast  released as many as 17
members of the former ruling party, including the ex-Defense
Minister Michel Amani N’Guessan and former Justice Minister
Yanon Yapo, the current minister of justice, Jeannot Ahoussou,
said by phone today.  Those released had been held under house arrest at the
hotel La Pergola.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Baudelaire Mieu in Abidjan at 
 bmieu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Philip Sanders at 
 psanders@bloomberg.net  